Description:
Views From Every Angle in the Stunning Palladio Complex
In the sensational Palladio residential complex from renowned architect Fender Katsalidis with stunning views from all aspects to match well-appointed style this two bedroom apartment right on the NewQuay waterfront gives you unprecedented access to all the Docklands has to offer.
Wonderfully presented and awash with natural light, this 18th floor apartment defines modern and relaxed living. A comfortable living and dining zone gives you views of the harbour as well as Etihad Stadium; enjoy these calming vistas further from your undercover balcony with a wine or beer in hand.
The contemporary kitchen features stainless steel appliances, ample storage and a breakfast bar for meals on the go. Both bedrooms offer built-in robes and have easy access to the tasteful white and crisp modern bathroom. Also enjoy the convenience of a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym, and private function area.
While you can enjoy all the perks of this stylish Docklands retreat, the location in the popular NewQuay Precinct takes your living experience to another level. You’ll have access to an array of superb local eateries including the infamous Berth and Cargo restaurants just to name a few. You’re also near Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, IGA supermarket, Costco, and the free trams stops are right at your door taking you to West Preston, Bundoora RMIT, the CBD and beyond.
Insights: 1807/15 Caravel Lane, Docklands VIC 3008 was last sold in 2017 and 275 other 2 bedroom unit in Docklands have recently been sold.

Description:
A Cut Above The Rest!
Flawlessly presented and built to the highest caliber, this near new Simonds home delivers a quality build, attention to the finest detail and a functional family friendly design. Designed to stand out with radiating visual appeal through its modern façade, making you want to call this home.
Making a statement from the moment you step inside with a wide hallway entrance drawing you inside the home. Tailored for entertaining with multiple living options, a formal lounge that leads to the spacious open plan living and dining. The sophisticated contemporary kitchen awaits, equipped with 900mm stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, Caesarstone benchtops, pendant lighting, glass splash-back and expansive walk in pantry, making this truly the heart of the home.
The grand master bedroom features a walk-in robe and a private ensuite with double sink and oversized shower. The remaining 3 great size bedrooms (all with BIRs) are serviced by the sparkling main bathroom.
Entertain in style outdoors by flowing on from the main living to provide the perfect combination of indoor-outdoor living on the oversized covered alfresco. Overlooking the low maintenance landscaped gardens with space for kids to enjoy, this is sure to complete your house hunting.
Offering impressive extra's, such as ducted heating, evaporative cooling, alarm system, quality flooring and tiling throughout, laundry and a double car garage with rear access and internal access.
Situated close to freeways, local schools, Derrimut Shopping Centre, cafes, restaurants, public transport and much more, this home has it all.
This beautiful home is not one to be missed and is ready for you to make memories of your own!

Description:
A Cut Above The Rest
Cutting edge in design and impeccably presented throughout, this unique family home adopts a contemporary approach to timeless family living. Defined by clean, considered lines and offering an abundance of natural light, this home is ideal for those seeking a warm, open and inviting home.
Upon arrival, the striking façade will immediately impress but it's once entering the front door that you'll truly appreciate the quality of the home beyond. The Gorgeous master bedroom sits at the front of the home featuring a walk-in-robe, stunning ensuite with double vanity and double doors with access outside.
The home offers multiple living zones including an informal front lounge, dining area and a large family room at the rear of the home overlooking the gardens beyond. The stunning streamlined kitchen is an entertainer's dream featuring stainless steel appliances, double ovens, walk-in pantry, ample bench space and an abundance of storage options. Sliding doors provide seamless access out to the undercover decking area and huge backyard perfect for year-round entertaining.
A further two bedrooms are all fitted with built-in robes and accompanied by a well-appointed central bathroom and separate toilet. Positioned on a corner block of 511m2 (approx.) and located near local shops, public transport, schools and parks as well as being just under 20klm from Melbourne CBD makes this location second to none!
Features include remote control double car garage, Evaporative cooling, ducted heating, hot water solar panels and much much more!

Description:
Luxury On a Spectacular Scale
If you're seeking a quality build where no expense has been spared, this unique offering to the market is one not to look past, with a list of features too long to list this one has to be seen to be believed. Custom built and Showcased by superior fixtures and fittings throughout, this contemporary home will impress those refusing to compromise. Captivating the moment you walk in and spread over 34 squares (approx.) of luxuriously vast space, This free-flowing family home is highlighted by features such as high ceilings, Sydney blue gum floorboards and downlights fitted throughout. Proudly positioned amongst the areas finest, this stunning residence sits on over 630sqm (approx) of premium Derrimut real estate
Showcasing a front formal lounge perfect for formal occasions or the option to create a 4th bedroom, huge rumpus room at the rear fitted with gas fireplace and sliding doors offering access out to the huge backyard. An expansive family domain incorporates an open plan living and dining room all designed on an impressive scale with sliding doors offering seamless access out to the concrete outdoor area- the opulent 'chef's' kitchen includes 'statement' island bench, quality stainless -steel appliances including smeg oven and cooktop as well as an abundance of workspace and well thought out storage solutions.
An impressive master bedroom with double door entry sits at the front of the home with WIR and ensuite featuring floor to ceiling tiles, double vanity and double shower - perfect for those seeking a luxury adobe. Zoned to the rear are two further double bedrooms, fully tiled family bathroom with double vanity, separate toilet plus a large laundry filled with endless storage options.
Some features include alarm, ducted heating, refrigerated air conditioning, split system, inbuilt vacuum system, downlights throughout, large double garage/storage with drive through access and plenty more. Located within close proximity to all Derrimut has to offer including Derrimut shopping village, Deer Park station, Freeway access and walking distance to St Lawrence primary school, parklands and Sunshine gold club, this is an opportunity not to be missed.

Reliance Real Estate Point Cook presents to you this 7 years young, Clearview Elite built home situated on a 458m2 (approx.) allotment. This modern and superb family home offers you a quality built atmosphere with upgraded fixtures and finishes complimenting the flowing floor plan, which will have you admiring how easy it is to navigate your way through the wide open spaces. The remaining 2 bedrooms are spacious in size and all including built in wardrobes for storage purposes and great natural light coming through. The central bathroom includes a great sized shower and bath that is fantastic for any sized family.
This family home is nothing short of close proximity to public transport, easy access to the freeway via the Western Freeway,
(1 km approx from the freeway)and only a short distance to local schools such as the Derrimut Primary School and St Laurence Catholic Primary School. Also walking distance to the Derrimut Village Shopping Centre, this home caters to your every need and you will have found an ideal home or investment opportunity.

Quality built, this stunning home offers a flowing floor plan that is both elegant and practical. Situated on a 650sqm block, homes like this are rare to find!
* 3 large bedrooms plus study and two bathrooms. Master bedroom with Walk In Robe and Ensuite with double vanity, shower and toilet.
* Multiple living areas include spacious formal lounge preceding expansive open plan informal living area incorporating hostess kitchen with quality stainless steel appliances including new oven, cooktop and rangehood, island bench with breakfast bar, ample workspace and storage including pantry. adjoining sun-filled dining and living room with access and outlook out to the entertaining area and garden beyond.

Description:
Desirable family home!
Welcoming upon entry and beautifully presented throughout, this unique single storey family home offers both character and finesse. From the moment you step inside, you'll instantly feel at home. Showcased by manicured gardens, an expansive outdoor area and beautiful features throughout, you won't look past this one.
This much-loved home features 2 separate living areas, a formal front loungeroom and a generous family/meal area allowing for both formal and informal entertaining options. The kitchen sits in the heart of the home offering great bench space, endless storage options, and quality stainless - steel appliances. Sliding doors provide seamless access to a beautiful undercover entertainment area overlooking the landscaped gardens.
The master bedroom is located at the rear of the home, completed with a walk-in robe and ensuite. With 3 Large bedrooms (all with B.I.R) and a study that can be converted into 4th bedroom if needed, this impressive home will surely tick all the boxes.
Features include remote control double car garage with internal access, solar panels, 2 split systems and ducted heating. Positioned opposite Derrimut Primary School on a massive 560m2 (approx.) block and located near local shops, public transport, schools and parks as well as being just under 20klm from Melbourne CBD makes this desirable family opportunity a must see!
Be quick to inspect this home!
